There's a sort of "management" hierarchy among the classes in
the packages `Communicator` and `Communicator.Mind`.

Communicator.Communicator (public, singleton)
  |-Communicator.CL*
  \-Communicator.Mind.Mind (public)
      |-Communicator.Mind.AddPageDoo
      \-Communicator.Mind.ClientConfiguration
          \-Communicator.Mind.Page
              \-Communicator.Mind.Widget
